@{B}@{FG Highlight}¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯@{UB}@{FG Text}
  RevFlex should run on any system running at least AmigaOS2.0 or higher.

  It comes with versions for each:
  - 68K AmigaOS
  - PPC AmigaOS4
  - PPC MorphOS

  The 68K version has been tested on WINUAE and on MorphOS via 68k emulation.

  The OS4 version has been tested on MorphOS using OS4Emu.

  The MorphOS version has been tested on MorphOS using MorphOS 3.17.

